{"tid":810341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"27歲嫩妻不願受精懷孕　87歲廢老男星宣布離婚","createTime":"2018-09-08T01:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T02:38:46.000Z","uid":72009,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1a86b732205b96d2b85cdfd17cfabaa27a16bcf9","tid":810341,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:52:18.000Z","msg":"現年87歲的俄羅斯老牌男演員柯拉斯克(Ivan Krasko)，在3年前宣布娶了小60歲的嫩妻雪薇爾(Natalia Shevel)，但近日柯拉斯克宣布，已和雪薇爾離婚，原因是雪薇爾不願意受精懷孕。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《都市報》報導，柯拉斯克已經演過140部影視作品與角色，在蘇聯時期也是知名演員，曾有過3段婚姻以及3子2女。就在2015年，柯拉斯克表示他和雪薇爾的師生戀修成正果，兩人完成終身大事。但近日柯拉斯克卻宣布，與雪薇爾離婚。<br />\n柯拉斯克解釋，雪薇爾從去年開始就拒絕和他做愛，原因是雪薇爾害怕因此受精懷孕。柯拉斯克說，他在去年表明很想跟雪薇爾生一個孩子，但雪薇爾一直認為兩人沒有足夠財力，無法養孩子，因此拒絕做愛懷孕。據悉雪薇爾出身貧困家庭，因此她很擔心自己的孩子會跟她有一樣的命運，她曾經向媒體表示：「生養孩子是一輩子的事，也代表著責任，我不想成為單親媽媽，也想要擁有私人空間。」<br />\n雪薇爾透露，她在西班牙度假期間收到被柯拉斯克離婚的消息。現在也傳出柯拉斯克想要回到第3任前妻維爾(Natalia Vyal)的身邊，維爾則為他生了2名兒子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180908/1426080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180908%2F1426080&d=NcR7R2YgvSmy%2FZlfdaZChf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0018fbdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180908%2F1426080&h=f6d47e7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180908/1426080</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180908/640_384fb818d48e83a6e8ac79121f047dc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180908%2F640_384fb818d48e83a6e8ac79121f047dc3.jpg&h=d80da522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180908/640_971cf21eafb4f72ee18e09a55d4ac854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180908%2F640_971cf21eafb4f72ee18e09a55d4ac854.jpg&h=83b2e61f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3911e09a1195b4f913b00490bc82d18f3a4f35","tid":810341,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:54:40.000Z","msg":"以為四哥"},{"pid":"3d8631c57a45ee93f64fab60181aedd14a18f727","tid":810341,"uid":182127,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:57:52.000Z","msg":"娶咗都冇得屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0434ac41bebcf5b401ce50d8ab3383ab0e3c7a","tid":810341,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d8631c57a45ee93f64fab60181aedd14a18f727","tid":810341,"uid":182127,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:57:52.000Z","msg":"娶咗都冇得屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:00:31.000Z","msg":"3 年前娶<br />\n去年先唔同佢做愛 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   點會無得屌呀 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ed7fc192dc01c459496e850bdcbb64674c6ec1","tid":810341,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:00:49.000Z","msg":"即刻分身家 生都唔洗生"},{"pid":"1a8a12ef194f437beccd0ef2224701771c4eba6c","tid":810341,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:04:52.000Z","msg":"柯拉斯克說，他在去年表明很想跟雪薇爾生一個孩子，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但雪薇爾一直認為兩人沒有足夠財力，無法養孩子</strong></span>，因此拒絕做愛懷孕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要咩財力先算夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9ec69953e15229e247e594c486dd3e53e44cdc","tid":810341,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0434ac41bebcf5b401ce50d8ab3383ab0e3c7a","tid":810341,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d8631c57a4